{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ValidityState.stepMismatch","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState/stepMismatch","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>stepMismatch</code></strong> は <strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></strong> オブジェクトの読み取り専用プロパティで、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> の値がユーザーに変更された後、その要素の <code>step</code> 属性に設定された制約に適合しないことを示します。</p>\n<p>フィールドが数値の性質を持つ場合、例えば <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/date\">date</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/month\">month</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/week\">week</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/time\">time</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/datetime-local\">datetime-local</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/number\">number</a>, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input/range\">range</a> の何れかの型であり、 step の値が <code>any</code> ではなく、値が <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Attributes/step\"><code>step</code></a> と <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Attributes/min\"><code>min</code></a> の値に設定された制約に適合しない場合に、 <code>stepMismatch</code> が true になります。フォームコントロールの値から <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Attributes/min\"><code>min</code></a> の値を引き、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Attributes/step\"><code>step</code></a> 値 (省略時は既定で 1) がゼロでない場合、一致しないと言えます。</p>\n<p>次のようになっていたとします。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">min</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">max</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>40<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">step</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code>(value - min) % 2 != 0</code> であれば、 <code>stepMismatch</code> は true になります。</p>\n<p><code>true</code> の場合、その要素は CSS の <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/:invalid\"><code>:invalid</code></a> および <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/CSS/:out-of-range\"><code>:out-of-range</code></a> 擬似クラスに一致します。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/form-control-infrastructure.html#dom-validitystate-stepmismatch","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.ValidityState.stepMismatch"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.ValidityState.stepMismatch","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState/stepMismatch/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Constraint_validation\">制約検証</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/Forms/Form_validation\">フォーム: データフォームの検証</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Attributes/step\"><code>step</code> 属性</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"stepMismatch は ValidityState オブジェクトの読み取り専用プロパティで、 <input> の値がユーザーに変更された後、その要素の step 属性に設定された制約に適合しないことを示します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ValidityState.stepMismatch","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ValidityState.stepMismatch","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/validitystate/stepmismatch","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/validitystate/stepmismatch/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState","title":"ValidityState"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/ValidityState/stepMismatch","title":"ValidityState.stepMismatch"}],"pageTitle":"ValidityState.stepMismatch - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}